title: I finally got around to watching Deadpool
body:
And I got carded by the dude taking tickets for the first time in my life I was like o_o 

Also I messed up and went to 7pm viewing so it was more expensive. Should've went to the matinee. Cost me 15 bux for ticket plus food 

Overall it was a solid movie.
